<subSubSection lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="489" pageId="3" pageNumber="488" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1836,2043]" lastBlockId="4.[151,1437,151,213]" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="489" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,493,1944,1970]" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Distribution and ecology</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[507,589,1944,1970]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1880,1904]" captionTargetBox="[307,1281,181,1843]" captionTargetId="figure-17@5.[307,1281,181,1856]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 4. Nemoura habitats in Qinghai, China. A. Habitat of Nemoura jixiangwangi sp. nov. and Nemoura securigera Klapálek, 1907: Deqian Village. B. Habitat of Nemoura jixiangwangi sp. nov.: Dayu Village. C. Habitat of Nemoura geei Wu, 1929 and Nemoura papilla Okamoto, 1922: Sigou. D. Habitat of Nemoura papilla Okamoto, 1922: Huzhu County, Weibei Highway. E–F. Habitat of Nemoura securigera Klapálek, 1907: Qihankaigou (Qihankai valley), main river and sidestream." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6899855" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6899855/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Fig. 4c</figureCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[638,708,1944,1970]" name="China" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">China</collectingCountry>
, the species is known from the 
<collectingRegion box="[1056,1192,1944,1970]" country="China" name="Nei Mongol" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Nei Mongol</collectingRegion>
Autonomous Region, 
<collectingRegion box="[151,236,1980,2006]" country="China" name="Beijing" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Beijing</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[252,328,1981,2007]" country="China" name="Henan" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Henan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[343,433,1980,2006]" country="China" name="Qinghai" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Qinghai</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[495,607,1980,2006]" country="China" name="Shandong" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Shandong</collectingRegion>
provinces (
<bibRefCitation author="Yang, D. &amp; Li, W. H." box="[745,946,1980,2006]" pageId="3" pageNumber="488" refId="ref4770" refString="Yang, D. &amp; Li, W. H. (2018) Species Catalogue of China. Volume 2 Animals, Insecta (III), Plecoptera. Science Press, Beijing, 71 pp." type="book" year="2018">Yang &amp; Li 2018</bibRefCitation>
). It is also known from 
<collectingCountry box="[1235,1302,1981,2007]" name="Japan" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Japan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1316,1384,1981,2007]" name="South Korea" pageId="3" pageNumber="488">Korea</collectingCountry>
and the Russian Far East (
<bibRefCitation author="Shimizu, T." box="[405,568,2016,2042]" pageId="3" pageNumber="488" pagination="193 - 218" refId="ref4100" refString="Shimizu, T. (1997) The species of the Nemoura ovocercia group (Plecoptera: Nemouridae). Aquatic Insects, 19 (4), 193 - 218. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 01650429709361656" type="journal article" year="1997">Shimizu 1997</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Zwick, P." box="[582,722,2016,2042]" pageId="3" pageNumber="488" pagination="75 - 97" refId="ref5042" refString="Zwick, P. (2010) New species and new records of Plecoptera from Korea and the Russian Far East. Illiesia, 6 (9), 75 - 97. [http: // www 2. pms-lj. si / illiesia / Illiesia 06 - 09. pdf]" type="journal article" year="2010">Zwick 2010</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Zhiltzova, L. A." box="[735,913,2016,2042]" pageId="3" pageNumber="488" refId="ref4982" refString="Zhiltzova, L. A. (2003) Vesnyanki (Plecoptera) gruppa Euholognatha. Nauka, St. Petersburg, 538 pp." type="book" year="2003">Zhiltzova 2003</bibRefCitation>
). This widespread species is new for Qinghai Province. It was collected by our hemipterologist colleague, Dr. Bin Zhang, from forest streams while searching for leafhoppers (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1825" box="[296,443,187,213]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cicadellidae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
